#: ../../../src/reference/security/data-protection.md:11
msgid ""
"In addition to purely technical security measures we implement additional "
"measures to provide a safe environment for your and your customers' data based "
"on the following standards and regulations:"
msgstr ""
"Neben rein technischen Sicherheitsmaßnahmen implementieren wir zusätzliche "
"Maßnahmen, um eine sichere Umgebung für deine und die Daten deiner Kunden zu "
